sherpa-onnx
==========

Project: sherpa-onnx
Upstream: https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx
License: Apache-2.0 (see upstream)

Usage in LanXin-MNN-Refactor:
- Android AAR (static-link onnxruntime) is downloaded at build time into voice/libs/
  (not committed to git). Task: :voice:downloadSherpaOnnxAar
- Default version: 1.13.4
  artifact: sherpa-onnx-static-link-onnxruntime-1.13.4.aar
- Override: SHERPA_ONNX_AAR (local path) or SHERPA_ONNX_AAR_URL
- ASR/TTS model files are external on device under:
  Android/data/com.lanxin.refactor/files/models/asr/
  Android/data/com.lanxin.refactor/files/models/tts/
  (not packaged in APK, not in git)

JNI library name: libsherpa-onnx-jni.so
Kotlin package (AAR): com.k2fsa.sherpa.onnx
LanXin wrapper package: com.lanxin.voice.sherpa
